@startuml
title Settings: Delete one face or erase all data (on-device)

actor User
participant "Home\nScreen" as Home
participant "Settings\nScreen" as Settings
participant "Room\nDB" as DB

User -> Home : Open Application
Home -> Settings : Open settings

Settings -> DB : Load registered faces
DB --> Settings : Face list

alt Delete single face
Settings -> DB : Delete face template (Face i)
DB --> Settings : Deleted
Settings --> User : Update list / show confirmation
else Erase all data
Settings -> DB : Delete all face templates
DB --> Settings : Deleted
Settings --> User : Show "All data erased" / empty list
end

User -> Settings : Close (X)
Settings -> Home : Return to home

@enduml
